                                    <h4>Increasing Interest-Free Student Loans</h4>
                                    <p>Increasing Canada Student and Apprentice Loans and Grants, because everyone who
                                        wants to go to school should have the support they need to cover the costs.</p>
                                </div>

                            </div>

                            <div class="col-md-4 mid">
                                <div class="eqht-trgt well white-well">
                                    <h4>More Work Experience and Skills Training for Youth</h4>
                                    <p>Helping young Canadians develop the skills and gain the work experience they need
                                        to achieve their dreams and get a good-paying job.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-md-4">
